  -But you know what, Shima?
  -Hm?

00:00:42.937 --> 00:00:45.173 position:5% line:83% align:start
As much as I hate to see Misae
get her heart broken,

00:00:45.273 --> 00:00:48.841 position:5% line:83% align:start
I think a guy like you suits her
a lot better than Igarashi.

00:00:48.941 --> 00:00:52.010 position:5% line:83% align:start
