 [sigh]

00:02:36.250 --> 00:02:37.617 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:02:49.792 --> 00:02:52.627 position:27% line:83% align:start
  -Sagara...
  -[gasp]

00:02:52.727 --> 00:02:55.730 position:50% line:83% align:start
Shima, what are
you doing here?

00:02:55.830 --> 00:03:00.833 position:5% line:83% align:start
Um, Sagara, I...
I mean, Misae, I, uh...

00:03:02.201 --> 00:03:03.436 position:61% line:89% align:start
 What is it?

00:03:03.536 --> 00:03:06.304 position:5% line:83% align:start
Love is like the fireworks
of days long past,

00:03:06.404 --> 00:03:07.372 position:5% line:89% align:start
don't you think?

00:03:07.472 --> 00:03:08.739 position:38% line:89% align:start
  What do you mean?

00:03:08.839 --> 00:03:11.307 position:5% line:83% align:start
Boom! You can't appreciate
its true beauty

00:03:11.408 --> 00:03:12.707 position:5% line:89% align:start
until it bursts.

00:03:12.808 --> 00:03:15.343 position:16% line:83% align:start
 Are you picking
 a fight with me, or what?!

00:03:15.444 --> 00:03:16.545 position:5% line:89% align:start
Sorry, sorry!

00:03:16.644 --> 00:03:18.412 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [sigh]

00:03:18.512 --> 00:03:21.581 position:5% line:83% align:start
Um... here...
you can use this.

00:03:21.681 --> 00:03:23.249 position:50% line:83% align:start
Use it for what?
I'm not crying.

00:03:23.349 --> 00:03:26.118 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, uh... Then use it when you
run out of toilet paper.

00:03:26.218 --> 00:03:30.321 position:5% line:83% align:start
Are you trying to be nice or are
you just trying to piss me off?!

00:03:31.388 --> 00:03:33.622 position:38% line:83% align:start
Why are you being
so weird, huh?

00:03:33.722 --> 00:03:36.525 position:38% line:83% align:start
I bet Yuki and Saki
put you up to this.

00:03:36.624 --> 00:03:38.860 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, could you tell?

00:03:38.960 --> 00:03:42.563 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're not the type to use
cheesy pickup lines like that.

00:03:42.662 --> 00:03:44.197 position:38% line:83% align:start
Why don't you try
saying something

00:03:44.297 --> 00:03:46.099 position:27% line:89% align:start
 from the heart instead?

00:03:47.833 --> 00:03:49.867 position:5% line:89% align:start
Uh, let's see...

00:03:51.235 --> 00:03:52.969 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:03:54.137 --> 00:03:56.339 position:27% line:83% align:start
 Why are you apologizing
 this time?

00:03:56.439 --> 00:03:57.840 position:5% line:89% align:start
Because...

00:03:57.940 --> 00:04:00.342 position:5% line:83% align:start
because I think it's probably
my fault that you're sad,

00:04:00.442 --> 00:04:01.509 position:5% line:89% align:start
at least on some level.

00:04:01.609 --> 00:04:03.211 position:38% line:83% align:start
What's that supposed
to mean?

00:04:03.311 --> 00:04:05.912 position:27% line:83% align:start
What makes you think you
did something wrong?

00:04:07.447 --> 00:04:08.746 position:27% line:89% align:start
 Wait, I take that back.

00:04:08.848 --> 00:04:10.549 position:27% line:83% align:start
 You've done pretty much
 everything wrong...

00:04:10.648 --> 00:04:12.649 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm really sorry!

00:04:13.817 --> 00:04:16.286 position:27% line:83% align:start
Anyway, it's not all the
stupid stuff you've done

00:04:16.386 --> 00:04:17.787 position:16% line:89% align:start
  that I'm depressed about.

00:04:17.887 --> 00:04:20.622 position:27% line:83% align:start
 This really has nothing
 to do with you.

00:04:20.722 --> 00:04:22.157 position:5% line:89% align:start
I see...

00:04:22.257 --> 00:04:25.359 position:5% line:83% align:start
Wait, don't tell me you're
thinking this is your big chance

00:04:25.459 --> 00:04:27.093 position:27% line:83% align:start
to make me fall
in love with you.

00:04:27.193 --> 00:04:29.395 position:16% line:83% align:start
Like we were talking about
yesterday, I mean.

00:04:29.496 --> 00:04:33.365 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's not fair, Misae. I wasn't
thinking about that at all.

00:04:36.234 --> 00:04:37.468 position:5% line:89% align:start
No, you're right.

00:04:37.568 --> 00:04:40.736 position:5% line:83% align:start
You just came here to do me
a favor, like you said before.

00:04:40.836 --> 00:04:42.404 position:38% line:83% align:start
You're not in love
with me or anything,

00:04:42.505 --> 00:04:44.672 position:16% line:83% align:start
 you're just doing what you
 think is right, aren't you?

00:04:44.772 --> 00:04:47.274 position:5% line:83% align:start
  -That's not true, either!
  -Huh?

00:04:50.810 --> 00:04:52.644 position:38% line:89% align:start
Well, okay then...

00:04:52.744 --> 00:04:56.680 position:27% line:83% align:start
So I guess... you are in
love with me, after all?

00:04:57.616 --> 00:04:59.150 position:5% line:89% align:start
I guess...

00:05:00.417 --> 00:05:02.285 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well... that settles it.

00:05:08.755 --> 00:05:13.025 position:5% line:83% align:start
By the way,
what do you like about me?

00:05:13.125 --> 00:05:15.060 position:38% line:83% align:start
Even if you scold me
all the time...

00:05:15.161 --> 00:05:17.428 position:16% line:83% align:start
 I know it's only
 because you care about me.

00:05:17.529 --> 00:05:20.063 position:16% line:83% align:start
  Oh, and when you do those
  wrestling moves on me...

00:05:20.164 --> 00:05:22.665 position:27% line:83% align:start
  you smell really nice
  and sweet.

00:05:22.765 --> 00:05:24.600 position:61% line:89% align:start
I like that.

00:05:24.699 --> 00:05:27.402 position:5% line:83% align:start
I think I could've done
without that last part.

00:05:28.069 --> 00:05:30.437 position:61% line:89% align:start
Sorry.

00:05:30.539 --> 00:05:32.839 position:5% line:89% align:start
You don't need to apologize.

00:05:33.374 --> 00:05:34.908 position:27% line:89% align:start
 [Shima sighs]

00:05:36.008 --> 00:05:37.075 position:5% line:89% align:start
Um...

00:05:38.177 --> 00:05:39.810 position:5% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:05:40.646 --> 00:05:44.047 position:50% line:83% align:start
You're welcome.
My pleasure...

00:05:46.749 --> 00:05:48.184 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Saki]
Misae!

00:05:49.185 --> 00:05:51.019 position:5% line:89% align:start
 [laughs] Hey, you free today?

00:05:51.119 --> 00:05:53.655 position:5% line:83% align:start
I heard there's a new ice cream
parlor across from the station.

00:05:53.754 --> 00:05:55.688 position:16% line:83% align:start
You wanna go
check it out with us?

00:05:55.788 --> 00:05:58.124 position:5% line:89% align:start
Sorry! I can't go today.

00:05:58.224 --> 00:06:00.559 position:5% line:83% align:start
Look. He's been waiting
out there all day.

00:06:00.660 --> 00:06:02.027 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'd feel bad if I left him
hanging

00:06:02.127 --> 00:06:03.327 position:5% line:89% align:start
and went off with you guys.

00:06:03.427 --> 00:06:04.727 position:5% line:89% align:start
See ya.

00:06:05.995 --> 00:06:07.864 position:27% line:83% align:start
It looks like those two
are getting along.

00:06:07.964 --> 00:06:10.532 position:16% line:83% align:start
She sure perked up,
that's for sure.

00:06:10.633 --> 00:06:12.234 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Shima]
Student council president?

00:06:12.334 --> 00:06:15.002 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's right. I know it doesn't
seem like it, but that's me.

00:06:15.102 --> 00:06:17.770 position:5% line:83% align:start
 And the first female president
 at the school, too.

00:06:17.871 --> 00:06:19.772 position:5% line:89% align:start
Wow, Misae, that's amazing!

00:06:19.872 --> 00:06:22.040 position:16% line:83% align:start
The Autumn Festival's right
around the corner.

00:06:22.141 --> 00:06:23.775 position:27% line:83% align:start
I have to help out
at the school,

00:06:23.875 --> 00:06:25.476 position:27% line:83% align:start
so I'm afraid I'm a
little busy right now.

00:06:25.577 --> 00:06:28.412 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sorry, I wish we could spend
a bit more time together.

00:06:28.512 --> 00:06:29.779 position:5% line:89% align:start
Autumn Festival?

00:06:29.879 --> 00:06:31.113 position:50% line:89% align:start
  By the way...

00:06:31.214 --> 00:06:33.748 position:27% line:83% align:start
I was thinking,
if you weren't too busy,

00:06:33.848 --> 00:06:36.183 position:27% line:83% align:start
maybe you and I could
check it out together.

00:06:36.283 --> 00:06:37.985 position:50% line:89% align:start
Like a date?

