00:06:43.590 --> 00:06:44.690 position:16% line:89% align:start
 [student] She's cute!

00:06:44.789 --> 00:06:46.757 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Saki] Don't worry!
You look great!

00:06:47.791 --> 00:06:50.327 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Shima] I see.
Misae's busy today, huh?

00:06:50.427 --> 00:06:53.295 position:5% line:83% align:start
