Oh, come on, ladies,
don't by shy.

00:07:39.327 --> 00:07:41.829 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's not like I'm hitting on
her, I'm just trying to be nice!

00:07:41.929 --> 00:07:43.264 position:5% line:89% align:start
Really, I think we're fine.

00:07:43.364 --> 00:07:45.366 position:5% line:83% align:start
-Run away! This is your chance!
-Tell me your name.

00:07:45.466 --> 00:07:47.166 position:5% line:83% align:start
-What class are you in?
-I'm telling you, we're fine!

00:07:47.267 --> 00:07:50.002 position:5% line:83% align:start
 Hey, wait a second, come back!
 I just wanna talk!

00:07:54.071 --> 00:07:56.473 position:5% line:89% align:start
