00:07:56.573 --> 00:07:58.007 position:16% line:89% align:start
Students bringing in guitars

00:07:58.107 --> 00:07:59.842 position:38% line:83% align:start
and making noise
in the classrooms.

00:07:59.942 --> 00:08:01.843 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't mind if they want
to sing quietly...

00:08:01.943 --> 00:08:03.911 position:5% line:83% align:start
But maybe they should apply for
a club permit.

00:08:04.012 --> 00:08:05.413 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Shima] <i>She's so cool...</i>

