Do you have some business
with the student council?

00:08:09.282 --> 00:08:11.883 position:5% line:83% align:start
There's no need to be so shy,
you can go inside if you like.

00:08:11.983 --> 00:08:14.985 position:5% line:83% align:start
There's no rule against it;
they're just having a meeting.

00:08:15.085 --> 00:08:17.154 position:5% line:89% align:start
Um, yeah, but I, uh, well...

00:08:17.254 --> 00:08:18.722 position:16% line:83% align:start
 -So I think-
 -Excuse me, Sagara...

00:08:18.821 --> 00:08:21.591 position:38% line:89% align:start
  Oh, Miss Ibuki...

00:08:21.691 --> 00:08:25.226 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry for interrupting.
This girl wants to talk to you.

00:08:25.960 --> 00:08:27.194 position:16% line:89% align:start
Go on, speak up...

00:08:27.295 --> 00:08:28.596 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:08:28.696 --> 00:08:31.298 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh my gosh, you're so cute!

00:08:31.398 --> 00:08:33.666 position:5% line:83% align:start
Sorry if I kept you
waiting too long.

00:08:33.766 --> 00:08:36.833 position:16% line:89% align:start
No, it's fine. Th-thank you.

00:08:36.934 --> 00:08:39.136 position:5% line:83% align:start
Anyway, what did you
want to talk about?

00:08:39.236 --> 00:08:41.571 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't hold back,
you can say anything.

00:08:41.672 --> 00:08:42.938 position:5% line:89% align:start
