00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:45.106 position:5% line:83% align:start
to listen to whatever the
students have to say.

00:08:46.574 --> 00:08:48.175 position:38% line:89% align:start
I, uh...

00:08:48.275 --> 00:08:49.410 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:08:49.510 --> 00:08:51.211 position:27% line:89% align:start
 I'll just say it then.

00:08:51.312 --> 00:08:53.246 position:16% line:89% align:start
Misae, I...

00:08:53.346 --> 00:08:55.715 position:5% line:83% align:start
I want to spend the
rest of my life with you...

00:08:55.814 --> 00:08:57.915 position:27% line:89% align:start
Right by your side.

00:08:59.317 --> 00:09:03.219 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry... What kind of
relationship do you two have?

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:04.754 position:27% line:89% align:start
[awkward laugh]

00:09:04.853 --> 00:09:07.056 position:27% line:89% align:start
 I think I'd better go!

00:09:08.424 --> 00:09:12.559 position:27% line:89% align:start
  [laughing]

00:09:14.161 --> 00:09:17.063 position:16% line:83% align:start
 Wow, that was the funniest
 thing I've ever seen.

00:09:17.163 --> 00:09:18.798 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's not funny at all!

00:09:18.897 --> 00:09:21.666 position:5% line:83% align:start
I wonder if she knew
it was me or not.

00:09:21.766 --> 00:09:23.801 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's all right, don't worry!

00:09:23.900 --> 00:09:25.134 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Yuki] But that
made me wonder...

00:09:25.234 --> 00:09:27.036 position:16% line:83% align:start
do you think Misae
likes you better that way?

00:09:27.136 --> 00:09:29.538 position:5% line:83% align:start
I hope that's supposed
to be a joke!

00:09:32.907 --> 00:09:34.742 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, that's right.

00:09:34.841 --> 00:09:36.576 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'd forgotten...

00:09:38.977 --> 00:09:41.413 position:27% line:83% align:start
 [Saki] Hey, Shima,
 are you busy right now?

00:09:41.513 --> 00:09:42.847 position:16% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:42.947 --> 00:09:45.349 position:16% line:83% align:start
Saki and I were cooking up
a little plan, that's all.

00:09:45.449 --> 00:09:48.284 position:5% line:83% align:start
If you're not busy, could we
go over to your house, please?

00:09:48.384 --> 00:09:50.519 position:5% line:89% align:start
What?!

00:09:50.619 --> 00:09:53.388 position:16% line:83% align:start
 [Saki] I see. Misae hasn't
 been to your house yet?

00:09:53.488 --> 00:09:54.988 position:27% line:89% align:start
 That's funny!

00:09:56.190 --> 00:09:57.491 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Yuki] Wow, you know,

00:09:57.591 --> 00:09:59.492 position:5% line:83% align:start
I was gonna brag about going
over to Shima's house

00:09:59.592 --> 00:10:00.793 position:5% line:89% align:start
while she was at school,

00:10:00.892 --> 00:10:02.227 position:5% line:89% align:start
but this is even better!

00:10:02.327 --> 00:10:03.562 position:27% line:89% align:start
  [laughing]

00:10:04.463 --> 00:10:05.863 position:27% line:89% align:start
 [Shima sighs]

00:10:08.064 --> 00:10:11.934 position:5% line:83% align:start
Is something wrong?
We don't have to tell Misae...

00:10:12.034 --> 00:10:14.570 position:27% line:89% align:start
No... That's not that.

00:10:15.703 --> 00:10:20.073 position:5% line:83% align:start
For some reason I can't remember
where my house is.

00:10:23.142 --> 00:10:25.510 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Saki] Hey, come on...
it's right over here!

00:10:25.610 --> 00:10:28.912 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't joke around like that,
it's not funny! Jeez!

00:10:29.012 --> 00:10:30.581 position:27% line:89% align:start
[door opens]

00:10:30.681 --> 00:10:32.014 position:27% line:89% align:start
 [gasp]

00:10:32.115 --> 00:10:34.916 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, hello, may I help you?

00:10:35.016 --> 00:10:36.451 position:72% line:89% align:start
 Hello!

00:10:36.551 --> 00:10:40.120 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey, what's wrong?
Stop spacing out and say hello!

00:10:41.321 --> 00:10:44.223 position:5% line:83% align:start
I see.
Are you Katsuki's friends?

00:10:44.323 --> 00:10:45.424 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yes, ma'am!

00:10:45.524 --> 00:10:46.859 position:16% line:89% align:start
I didn't know.

00:10:46.958 --> 00:10:49.160 position:5% line:83% align:start
Thank you for coming
all this way.

00:10:49.260 --> 00:10:51.128 position:5% line:89% align:start
Make yourselves at home.

00:10:51.228 --> 00:10:54.498 position:5% line:83% align:start
You can offer him some incense
at the altar, if you like.

00:10:54.598 --> 00:10:56.132 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [gasp]

00:10:59.234 --> 00:11:02.436 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>That's right...</i>
 <i>I remember now.</i>

00:11:02.536 --> 00:11:05.972 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>The real Katsuki Shima</i>
 <i>isn't here anymore.</i>

00:11:06.072 --> 00:11:11.008 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I... I'm not actually</i>
 <i>Katsuki Shima...</i>

00:11:14.612 --> 00:11:16.246 position:27% line:83% align:start
 -Hey, wait!
 -Ah!

00:11:26.119 --> 00:11:29.488 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Yuki] Hey, Shima,
what's going on?

00:11:29.588 --> 00:11:32.056 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Saki] It's okay if you
don't want to tell us.

00:11:32.157 --> 00:11:35.159 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah, is there anything
we can do for you?

00:11:37.528 --> 00:11:41.096 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey, At the very least,
remember this.

00:11:41.196 --> 00:11:44.800 position:5% line:83% align:start
We believe you. We know you
must have your reasons.

00:11:44.900 --> 00:11:46.300 position:5% line:89% align:start
It doesn't matter what happened.

00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:48.701 position:16% line:83% align:start
To us, you're the one
and only Shima.

00:11:48.802 --> 00:11:50.670 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's right,
you're still our friend

00:11:50.770 --> 00:11:52.471 position:5% line:89% align:start
and that's all that matters.

00:11:53.472 --> 00:11:54.706 position:61% line:89% align:start
 Thank you.

00:11:54.807 --> 00:11:57.474 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Yuki] Don't worry,
we won't say anything to Misae.

00:11:57.575 --> 00:11:59.876 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Saki] You can tell her
whatever you need to tell her.

00:12:00.009 --> 00:12:02.011 position:5% line:89% align:start
We'll leave it up to you.

00:12:08.816 --> 00:12:14.052 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I finally remembered.</i>
 <i>I'm not Katsuki Shima at all.</i>

00:12:14.152 --> 00:12:16.888 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>He was someone</i>
 <i>very special to me.</i>

00:12:16.987 --> 00:12:20.390 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Someone I spent</i>
 <i>a long time with.</i>

00:12:20.490 --> 00:12:24.560 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I can see his face...</i>
 <i>I remember his words...</i>

00:12:24.660 --> 00:12:26.261 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>But he's gone now.</i>

00:12:26.361 --> 00:12:28.629 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>He entrusted me</i>
 <i>with his final wish.</i>

00:12:28.729 --> 00:12:31.498 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>The reason I came here</i>
 <i>was to grant him that wish.</i>

00:12:31.598 --> 00:12:34.099 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>And now that I've seen the</i>
 <i>world through his eyes...</i>

00:12:34.200 --> 00:12:37.669 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I understand why</i>
 <i>it was so important.</i>

00:12:42.806 --> 00:12:45.608 position:5% line:89% align:start
 Oh! You finally made it!

00:12:46.342 --> 00:12:48.677 position:16% line:89% align:start
 Yeah... Sorry I'm late!

00:12:48.777 --> 00:12:50.377 position:5% line:89% align:start
Nah. It's fine.

00:12:50.478 --> 00:12:53.914 position:5% line:83% align:start
The way I see it, it your turn
to make me wait for a change.

00:12:54.013 --> 00:12:55.515 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Misae chuckles]

00:12:57.149 --> 00:13:00.017 position:5% line:83% align:start
That girl at the meeting
yesterday was you, right?

00:13:00.117 --> 00:13:01.385 position:38% line:89% align:start
You figured it out?

00:13:01.486 --> 00:13:05.055 position:5% line:83% align:start
Of course I did!
We see each other every day!

00:13:05.155 --> 00:13:07.790 position:38% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry...
Was I bothering you?

00:13:07.891 --> 00:13:12.393 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's fine. I bet Yuki and Saki
put you up to it, anyway.

00:13:15.496 --> 00:13:17.296 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Misae] A wish?

00:13:17.396 --> 00:13:18.431 position:50% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:13:18.531 --> 00:13:21.700 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can't forget, that's
the reason I came here.

00:13:21.800 --> 00:13:26.336 position:16% line:83% align:start
Look, inside this, there's
a light that grants wishes.

00:13:26.436 --> 00:13:28.605 position:27% line:89% align:start
  Oh no... it's gone...

00:13:28.705 --> 00:13:31.907 position:5% line:83% align:start
Maybe there wasn't anything
in there to begin with.

00:13:32.006 --> 00:13:34.442 position:5% line:83% align:start
Maybe that means I don't
need a wish after all,

00:13:34.542 --> 00:13:36.544 position:5% line:83% align:start
or maybe it's already
been granted.

00:13:36.644 --> 00:13:39.479 position:5% line:83% align:start
Either way, let's not dwell on
this whole wish thing;

00:13:39.579 --> 00:13:41.514 position:5% line:83% align:start
all that matters is that
we're both happy.

00:13:41.614 --> 00:13:45.116 position:16% line:83% align:start
  But this...
  this is really important.

00:13:45.216 --> 00:13:47.484 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, if you insist.

00:13:47.584 --> 00:13:48.852 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh... I know!

00:13:48.952 --> 00:13:50.219 position:16% line:89% align:start
 Did you think of something?

00:13:50.319 --> 00:13:52.655 position:5% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm. I sure did.

00:13:52.755 --> 00:13:54.189 position:5% line:89% align:start
'Kay, this is it.

00:13:54.289 --> 00:13:56.658 position:5% line:83% align:start
Here comes the wish you've been
dying to hear for so long.

00:13:56.758 --> 00:13:58.492 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ready?

00:14:00.560 --> 00:14:02.027 position:5% line:89% align:start
I wish...

00:14:02.127 --> 00:14:04.029 position:5% line:89% align:start
for you to stay by my side

00:14:04.129 --> 00:14:06.030 position:5% line:89% align:start
and love me forever.

00:14:06.130 --> 00:14:07.431 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [gasp]

00:14:07.532 --> 00:14:10.033 position:5% line:83% align:start
Just like you said...
I want you here...

00:14:10.133 --> 00:14:14.236 position:5% line:83% align:start
loving me and caring for
me forever and ever.

00:14:14.336 --> 00:14:17.405 position:5% line:89% align:start
So, there you have it. My wish.

00:14:19.473 --> 00:14:20.807 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [gasp]

00:14:29.480 --> 00:14:31.815 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, did I surprise you?

00:14:38.453 --> 00:14:41.489 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I love her.</i>
 <i>I love her so much...</i>

00:14:41.589 --> 00:14:43.823 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I know we didn't</i>
 <i>spend long together,</i>

00:14:43.925 --> 00:14:47.192 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>but every moment was priceless.</i>

00:14:47.293 --> 00:14:49.728 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>I like Yuki and Saki, too.</i>

00:14:49.828 --> 00:14:51.896 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>All these memories...</i>

00:14:51.996 --> 00:14:55.799 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I really wish the four of us</i>
 <i>could stay together forever.</i>

00:14:55.899 --> 00:14:57.366 position:27% line:89% align:start
  [laughing]

00:14:57.466 --> 00:15:00.769 position:5% line:83% align:start
I was just copying what you
said yesterday, you know.

00:15:03.404 --> 00:15:06.406 position:5% line:83% align:start
Come on, why are you
crying so much?

00:15:06.506 --> 00:15:07.473 position:61% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry...

00:15:07.574 --> 00:15:09.842 position:5% line:83% align:start
I really have to look
after you, don't I?

00:15:09.943 --> 00:15:11.643 position:72% line:89% align:start
Misae...

00:15:12.343 --> 00:15:13.444 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:15:13.911 --> 00:15:15.580 position:61% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:15:16.479 --> 00:15:19.481 position:27% line:83% align:start
Thank you so much,
for everything.

00:15:21.617 --> 00:15:22.985 position:5% line:89% align:start
Ah...

00:15:23.084 --> 00:15:24.352 position:5% line:89% align:start
Uh, I, uh...

00:15:24.452 --> 00:15:26.753 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm going to get something
to drink, okay?

00:15:26.853 --> 00:15:28.055 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'll be right back.

00:15:28.154 --> 00:15:30.856 position:27% line:89% align:start
[quiet sobbing]

00:15:44.266 --> 00:15:45.767 position:27% line:89% align:start
 [worried sigh]

00:15:52.237 --> 00:15:53.772 position:5% line:89% align:start
Why is he...

00:15:55.574 --> 00:15:57.141 position:38% line:89% align:start
 Shima!

00:15:58.776 --> 00:16:00.143 position:38% line:89% align:start
 Shima!

00:16:00.243 --> 00:16:02.211 position:27% line:89% align:start
 [inaudible]

00:16:03.346 --> 00:16:06.381 position:5% line:89% align:start
I don't... What are you saying?

00:16:09.149 --> 00:16:10.784 position:5% line:89% align:start
Shima, wait!

00:16:16.588 --> 00:16:19.457 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Shima] <i>Good bye, Misae.</i>
 <i>I'm sorry.</i>

00:16:19.557 --> 00:16:22.258 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll do my best to</i>
 <i>grant your wish.</i>

00:16:22.359 --> 00:16:25.028 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>My feelings will never fade.</i>

00:16:25.127 --> 00:16:28.764 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll love you</i>
 <i>forever and ever...</i>

00:16:36.836 --> 00:16:38.771 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Misae] Yeah, I came back.

00:16:41.539 --> 00:16:44.273 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's right. The boy's dorm.

00:16:45.843 --> 00:16:49.244 position:16% line:83% align:start
No, I don't have any plans
like that right now.

00:16:49.344 --> 00:16:50.579 position:27% line:89% align:start
 [chuckling]

00:16:50.679 --> 00:16:52.747 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's not 'cause I'm still
thinking of him,

00:16:52.847 --> 00:16:54.515 position:5% line:89% align:start
it's just, you know...

00:16:54.615 --> 00:16:58.918 position:5% line:83% align:start
Well, what can you say, like it
or not, that's my life, right?

00:17:00.719 --> 00:17:02.453 position:5% line:89% align:start
Mm-hmm. Of course.

00:17:02.553 --> 00:17:06.790 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'd love to meet up sometime.
We'll invite Yuki, too. Bye.

00:17:11.060 --> 00:17:12.193 position:5% line:89% align:start
Don't suppose there's much hope

00:17:12.293 --> 00:17:14.996 position:5% line:83% align:start
of getting rid of you
at this point.

00:17:15.096 --> 00:17:17.131 position:5% line:83% align:start
Do you like being
with me that much?

00:17:17.230 --> 00:17:18.699 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [meow]

00:17:18.799 --> 00:17:22.167 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm not really at all fond
of cats, to be honest with you.

00:17:22.267 --> 00:17:23.935 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [meow]

00:17:26.804 --> 00:17:28.039 position:5% line:89% align:start
It can't be.

00:17:28.139 --> 00:17:31.573 position:5% line:83% align:start
Wow, I almost got lost in a
fairytale for a second there.

00:17:31.675 --> 00:17:33.375 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [meow]

00:17:33.475 --> 00:17:36.277 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're a weird cat...
you know that?

00:17:39.312 --> 00:17:42.682 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Nagisa] Tomoya...
Tomoya, wake up!

00:17:47.752 --> 00:17:50.521 position:5% line:83% align:start
I never knew you and the cat
had so much in common!

00:17:50.621 --> 00:17:53.489 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's getting late, Tomoya.
We should get going.

00:17:53.589 --> 00:17:54.957 position:61% line:89% align:start
Ah, yeah...

00:17:57.092 --> 00:17:58.259 position:16% line:89% align:start
Thank you so much.

00:17:58.359 --> 00:18:00.094 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry we ended up
staying so late.

00:18:00.193 --> 00:18:01.461 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Misae] No, it's fine.

00:18:01.561 --> 00:18:03.530 position:16% line:83% align:start
Just make sure you two go to
the Autumn Festival,

00:18:03.630 --> 00:18:04.530 position:50% line:89% align:start
like I said.

00:18:04.631 --> 00:18:05.597 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Nagisa] Okay!

00:18:05.698 --> 00:18:08.167 position:5% line:83% align:start
Were you the one who
showed me that dream?

00:18:08.266 --> 00:18:09.233 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [meow]

00:18:09.333 --> 00:18:10.802 position:27% line:89% align:start
  [chuckle]

00:18:10.902 --> 00:18:13.637 position:5% line:83% align:start
You already had a name
after all, didn't you?

00:18:13.737 --> 00:18:17.707 position:5% line:83% align:start
I get it, you want me to tell
Misae something for you, right?

00:18:27.613 --> 00:18:28.880 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Nagisa] Earth to Tomoya...

00:18:28.981 --> 00:18:30.482 position:38% line:83% align:start
-What's wrong?
-Huh?

00:18:30.582 --> 00:18:32.150 position:27% line:83% align:start
It seems like you've had
something on your mind

00:18:32.249 --> 00:18:33.684 position:38% line:89% align:start
  since last night.

00:18:33.784 --> 00:18:36.187 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yeah. There's something
I need to tell Misae,

00:18:36.286 --> 00:18:37.887 position:5% line:89% align:start
but I don't quite know how.

00:18:37.987 --> 00:18:39.354 position:61% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:42.323 --> 00:18:43.591 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [gasp]

00:18:43.691 --> 00:18:46.693 position:27% line:83% align:start
Misae's kitty came
to the festival, too!

00:18:47.761 --> 00:18:49.228 position:5% line:89% align:start
So what's the deal?

00:18:49.328 --> 00:18:51.529 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't tell me you have
something else you wanna say.

00:18:51.629 --> 00:18:53.263 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [meow]

00:18:53.364 --> 00:18:55.566 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Misae] Furukawa...
And her boyfriend!

00:18:55.666 --> 00:18:57.968 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, Misae!
Glad you could make it!

00:18:58.068 --> 00:18:59.602 position:38% line:83% align:start
Ah, thank goodness
you caught him!

00:18:59.702 --> 00:19:01.938 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Oh! I'm out of breath!
-I have a name, you know.

00:19:02.038 --> 00:19:04.106 position:16% line:83% align:start
You don't have to call me
"Furukawa's boyfriend."

00:19:04.206 --> 00:19:06.273 position:5% line:83% align:start
I have to admit, Misae,
it's pretty strange

00:19:06.373 --> 00:19:08.042 position:5% line:83% align:start
bringing your cat
to a festival.

00:19:08.142 --> 00:19:09.676 position:27% line:89% align:start
You got it all wrong.

00:19:09.776 --> 00:19:12.377 position:5% line:83% align:start
He ran out of the dorm all of
a sudden and wouldn't stop.

00:19:12.478 --> 00:19:15.013 position:27% line:83% align:start
I had to chase him all
the way to the festival.

00:19:15.114 --> 00:19:16.881 position:5% line:89% align:start
 Honestly, what was he thinking?

00:19:16.981 --> 00:19:19.549 position:27% line:89% align:start
  [meowing]

00:19:21.617 --> 00:19:23.819 position:27% line:83% align:start
I really have to look
after him, don't I?

00:19:23.919 --> 00:19:26.988 position:27% line:89% align:start
  [meowing]

00:19:27.088 --> 00:19:30.124 position:16% line:83% align:start
What's wrong?
Get out of there!

00:19:30.224 --> 00:19:31.791 position:5% line:83% align:start
-Come on!
-[Tomoya] I'm not surprised.

00:19:31.891 --> 00:19:33.693 position:5% line:83% align:start
-We're going home!
-He probably wanted to come

00:19:33.793 --> 00:19:36.293 position:5% line:83% align:start
to this festival with you
for a long time.

00:19:37.495 --> 00:19:40.197 position:27% line:83% align:start
Last night, when I fell
asleep at your place,

00:19:40.296 --> 00:19:42.799 position:16% line:89% align:start
I heard him speaking to me.

00:19:42.899 --> 00:19:44.100 position:27% line:89% align:start
He said he was sorry.

00:19:44.200 --> 00:19:47.301 position:5% line:83% align:start
He wanted to stay with you
until the end of the festival.

00:19:51.371 --> 00:19:55.674 position:5% line:83% align:start
Did he...
Did he say anything else?

00:19:55.775 --> 00:19:59.310 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah. He also said he'd stay
by your side and love you,

00:19:59.410 --> 00:20:01.311 position:27% line:89% align:start
  just like you wished.

00:20:06.015 --> 00:20:08.617 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't remember saying I'd take
a cat on a date.

00:20:08.717 --> 00:20:12.220 position:5% line:83% align:start
You've been so bad...
running me around.

00:20:12.319 --> 00:20:16.455 position:16% line:83% align:start
But... for once...
Let's just have fun.

00:20:18.258 --> 00:20:20.993 position:5% line:83% align:start
Also, Misae,
there's one more thing he said.

00:20:21.093 --> 00:20:22.227 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:20:22.326 --> 00:20:23.527 position:27% line:89% align:start
He said, no matter what,

00:20:23.627 --> 00:20:25.562 position:16% line:89% align:start
  he wants you to be happy.

00:20:26.663 --> 00:20:29.865 position:5% line:83% align:start
Go figure.
That's the kind of guy he is.

00:20:29.965 --> 00:20:31.499 position:5% line:89% align:start
All this time...

00:20:31.599 --> 00:20:34.035 position:5% line:83% align:start
he's been worried
about you, Misae.

00:20:36.435 --> 00:20:38.805 position:16% line:89% align:start
Worried? I see.

00:20:38.905 --> 00:20:40.405 position:16% line:89% align:start
I guess you're right.

00:20:40.505 --> 00:20:42.741 position:16% line:89% align:start
He is that kind of guy.

00:20:43.208 --> 00:20:44.475 position:27% line:89% align:start
 [chuckle]

00:20:44.575 --> 00:20:46.509 position:5% line:83% align:start
You were right,
I'm not old yet.

00:20:46.610 --> 00:20:48.711 position:5% line:89% align:start
I should enjoy my youth.

00:20:51.446 --> 00:20:53.115 position:27% line:89% align:start
 Tomoya, I don't get it.

00:20:53.215 --> 00:20:55.284 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't worry.
It was just a dream.

00:20:55.383 --> 00:20:58.085 position:5% line:83% align:start
I think you'd like
to hear about it, though.

00:20:58.186 --> 00:21:00.187 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's a little bittersweet...

00:21:00.287 --> 00:21:02.254 position:16% line:83% align:start
but I think it's a
wonderful love story.

00:21:02.354 --> 00:21:04.622 position:16% line:89% align:start
  [festival chatter]

00:21:14.063 --> 00:21:15.564 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Shima] <i>Katsuki...</i>

00:21:15.664 --> 00:21:18.300 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>I hope you can hear me.</i>

